#

Autumn Harvest Pumpkin Salad

45 min
$12
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

NutsDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SaladAutumnHealthy

Description

A warm, hearty salad filled with roasted pumpkin, fresh greens, and a hint of sweetness from cranberries, perfect for the fall.

Ingredients

  • pumpkin: 2 cups, cubed
  • mixed greens: 4 cups
  • cranberries: 1/2 cup, dried
  • feta cheese: 1/2 cup, crumbled
  • pecans: 1/3 cup, chopped
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • apple cider vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • honey: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • cinnamon: 1/2 teaspoon
